Package assignmenttests.classlevel.products.simulation

Class CBSIM

java.lang.Object
assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTestBase
assignmenttests.classlevel.products.simulation.CBSIM
All Implemented Interfaces:
assignmenttests.AssignmentTest, assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTest
@TestInstance(PER_CLASS) public class CBSIM extends assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTestBase
Class-level test for simulating and verifying assignment behavior. This test verifies method call counts and console output matches based on the assignment setup.

This test extends ClassTestBase and performs the following: - Verifies console outputs for correctness. - Ensures expected method calls are made during execution.
